<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
I've had an easy time raising 2hb up by soloing Snow Cougars in Iceclad.  Tactic I used was Malise/sick pet/slow/Poison/Haste self/melee.  With a 2hb of 50-70, I'd kill the cougar taking about 1-2 bubs of damage and 2-3 bubs of mana.  They do hit hard, but if you can do double the melee damage I did (not hard) I wouldn't see it as being a problem, as you'd kill them alot faster.<P>Exp at 35 here is slow, but that's why I've stayed.  I view the exp as a small bonus for raising my skills, and basically just camping Cougar Claw Earrings.  I was getting a drop about every 2 hours or so.  Carefull though, Cougar's are not too easy to pull, and people train them to the igloo's when they pull too many.<P>--------------------<P>Torbain - 35th Barbarian Warrior<BR>Tordain - 34th Barbarian Shaman<BR>Phynix  - 34th Dark Elf Magician<BR>Saryrn Server
