To bring defense up do the following.<P>Pull low easy blue (example: in OT tigeress instead of tiger or rhino) to zone.<P>Let mob hit you<BR>heal<BR>let mob hit you<BR>heal<BR>let mob hit you<BR>heal<BR>let mob hit you<BR>zone.<P>rinse and repeat.<P>--------------------<P>Greymyst<P>You all are just jealous because the voices only speak to me.
